The paper proposes a new image instance segmentation method using deep learning for gland histology images. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.LG) and the exploitation of complex multichannel information (cs.AI). The evaluation metrics used in the paper include Dice similarity coefficient (cs.IR) and mean average precision (cs.MM).
